			<div class="content" id="post-content-3831498">
									

<p>I like the density of references in here; they're subtle enough to integrate this piece firmly into the world without detracting from the story.</p>
<p>Tangential note: I find it interesting that people really seem to want to believe that 2718 isn't as horrifying as presented. This feels like the 2nd or 3rd time I've specifically heard the 'quantum retrocausality tech caused it' explanation.</p>

