<p>I really shouldn't upvote something with a blatant Python pastiche in it, but it was just carried off with such <em>panache</em>, and it was properly rewritten instead of being a find-and-replace job&#8230; The final few lines remind me of something too, but I can't quite work out what. The Young Ones, possibly?</p>
<p>Have my +1, dammit.</p>

